  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428840/extras/c0986e401749e471482c17e85ebd5570.poster.avif?t=1773309701\" width=800 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428840/extras/c0986e401749e471482c17e85ebd5570.webm?t=1773309701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428840/extras/c0986e401749e471482c17e85ebd5570.mp4?t=1773309701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Miniatures: An art house game collection</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play four hand-drawn memories from childhood and explore the strangeness and unease hiding beneath familiar moments. Some stories are mysterious, others whimsical, and all are a bit experimental. Each story is supported by its own unique art style and soundscape. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A short, open-to-interpretation experience with a total playtime of about <strong>30–40 minutes</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428840/extras/22aa843def8425faffb291e3075128a5.poster.avif?t=1773309701\" width=800 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428840/extras/22aa843def8425faffb291e3075128a5.webm?t=1773309701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428840/extras/22aa843def8425faffb291e3075128a5.mp4?t=1773309701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What's inside?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open up an old wooden box and discover four different objects: a screwdriver, a lizard, a seashell and a moth. Each one has its own story to tell:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 🪛 <strong><i>Familiar </i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assemble a curious cabinet together with your family. It is not as easy, as it seems.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>🦎 The Paludarium</i></strong><i> </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take care of your pet lizard while nature slowly creeps in. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>🦋 The House of the Moon</i></strong><i> </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search for the moon in a dark seascape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>🐚 The Last Sand Castle</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help the music-loving inhabitants of a sand castle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428840/extras/fcfb84e633f263dc001d65c8e1b95b7d.poster.avif?t=1773309701\" width=800 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428840/extras/fcfb84e633f263dc001d65c8e1b95b7d.webm?t=1773309701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428840/extras/fcfb84e633f263dc001d65c8e1b95b7d.mp4?t=1773309701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The experience</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Miniatures</i> is an atmospheric and slightly unsettling experience for players who enjoy narrative experimentation, stylised visuals and subtle, but poignant storytelling. It features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hand-drawn and award-winning art </strong>with a picture book aesthetic</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Short and impactful stories </strong>that are emotional and open to interpretation. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Atmospheric and ambient soundscapes</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Simple and easy interactions: </strong>point, click and explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428840/extras/2a81f58db37eb24e362eb4c2c4183c38.poster.avif?t=1773309701\" width=800 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428840/extras/2a81f58db37eb24e362eb4c2c4183c38.webm?t=1773309701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428840/extras/2a81f58db37eb24e362eb4c2c4183c38.mp4?t=1773309701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the moon, feed the lizard, and discover surreal childhood memories, where the familiar turns mysterious and strange. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428840/extras/c0986e401749e471482c17e85ebd5570.poster.avif?t=1773309701\" width=800 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428840/extras/c0986e401749e471482c17e85ebd5570.webm?t=1773309701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428840/extras/c0986e401749e471482c17e85ebd5570.mp4?t=1773309701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Miniatures: An art house game collection</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play four hand-drawn memories from childhood and explore the strangeness and unease hiding beneath familiar moments. Some stories are mysterious, others whimsical, and all are a bit experimental. Each story is supported by its own unique art style and soundscape. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A short, open-to-interpretation experience with a total playtime of about <strong>30–40 minutes</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428840/extras/22aa843def8425faffb291e3075128a5.poster.avif?t=1773309701\" width=800 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428840/extras/22aa843def8425faffb291e3075128a5.webm?t=1773309701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428840/extras/22aa843def8425faffb291e3075128a5.mp4?t=1773309701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What's inside?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open up an old wooden box and discover four different objects: a screwdriver, a lizard, a seashell and a moth. Each one has its own story to tell:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 🪛 <strong><i>Familiar </i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assemble a curious cabinet together with your family. It is not as easy, as it seems.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>🦎 The Paludarium</i></strong><i> </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take care of your pet lizard while nature slowly creeps in. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>🦋 The House of the Moon</i></strong><i> </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search for the moon in a dark seascape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>🐚 The Last Sand Castle</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help the music-loving inhabitants of a sand castle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428840/extras/fcfb84e633f263dc001d65c8e1b95b7d.poster.avif?t=1773309701\" width=800 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428840/extras/fcfb84e633f263dc001d65c8e1b95b7d.webm?t=1773309701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428840/extras/fcfb84e633f263dc001d65c8e1b95b7d.mp4?t=1773309701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The experience</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Miniatures</i> is an atmospheric and slightly unsettling experience for players who enjoy narrative experimentation, stylised visuals and subtle, but poignant storytelling. It features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hand-drawn and award-winning art </strong>with a picture book aesthetic</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Short and impactful stories </strong>that are emotional and open to interpretation. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Atmospheric and ambient soundscapes</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Simple and easy interactions: </strong>point, click and explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428840/extras/2a81f58db37eb24e362eb4c2c4183c38.poster.avif?t=1773309701\" width=800 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428840/extras/2a81f58db37eb24e362eb4c2c4183c38.webm?t=1773309701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428840/extras/2a81f58db37eb24e362eb4c2c4183c38.mp4?t=1773309701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the moon, feed the lizard, and discover surreal childhood memories, where the familiar turns mysterious and strange. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
